Class Pair<T1,T2>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.util.AssertedClass
      • sketch.util.Pair<T1,T2>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TprintTuple

    public class Pair<T1,T2>
extends AssertedClass
    Purpose: Store two Objects in a Single Object
    Description:
    This class is used to store an ordered pair of objects in a single object. The user can retrieve both objects and check equality of pairs. Objects stored can be null.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Michal Karczmarek
